com.portletguru.portlettester.mocks

Class PortletConfigGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.portletguru.portlettester.mocks.PortletConfigGenerator

  • public class PortletConfigGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to create a PortletConfig instance. It allows you to fill in the content usually defined in the portlet.xml file into a PortletConfig object, so that it can be used later to initialize a Portlet object.
